reviewText: Annoyed at having to wait for the next season to be released. This took me back to my childhood in that area. I could alsmost fell the atmosphere there again. Well done and believable characters. Brilliant.
I sure this is as good as the previous ones but it refuses to play in my dvd player.  I've tried several times but none of the discs will play.  I am not sure what to do.
None of the disks would play on my DVD player, had to mail them back awaiting my refund
